{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":21499,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"全国人大是干啥的？","timestamp":1592885391,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21509,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 演戏的","timestamp":1592885423,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21515,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我认为是没有的。CHN体制最大的问题不在于左和右，在于真和假","timestamp":1592885446,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21519,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"这个问题早该被讨论了。纪委只能向下监督。正国级中除一把手外，其他人会被一把手监督。那么一把手谁来监督？","timestamp":1592885458,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21522,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 橡皮图章","timestamp":1592885458,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21525,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"政治确实不是那样容易就能说清楚的","timestamp":1592885472,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21549,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"有，长老们之间会有制衡的，比如李和习","timestamp":1592885568,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21551,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"历史和后人的评价","timestamp":1592885577,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21554,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"主要是“最高领导人”这个位置从二共开始就是个和实权脱钩的虚职，因此也没必要有配套监督机制；\n所以现在是实权回来了但是配套制衡机制没跟上","timestamp":1592885588,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21562,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Grace: 那是九龙治水的事能相互制衡。现在定于一尊如何制衡？","timestamp":1592885619,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21564,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"一把手也不是从天而降的，恰恰就是在制衡中被推举出来的最具有协调和驾驭能力的人。","timestamp":1592885648,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21579,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"即使所有人都受到监督，整个体系跑偏也不是没有（比如现在的大明","timestamp":1592885755,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21585,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Isabella: 所以只要选上来就没有制衡了？ 一考定终身。。","timestamp":1592885794,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21597,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Isabella: 革命成功之后怎么办？一把手选上之后呢？就不会变化？","timestamp":1592885876,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21616,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"退位的前几任手里还算是有一定权力的吧","timestamp":1592885961,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":21730,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Louis","permissions":["report"],"pid":3645,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"以前是政治局+政治老人 但是听说现在民主集中制已经被破坏了","timestamp":1592886483,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":13,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":3645,"reply":16,"tag":"政治相关","text":"我国政治体制中对于最高领导人到底有没有监督和制衡，如果有，程度怎样？键政小白想问问大家的看法","timestamp":1592885361,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782585,"url":"","vote":{}}}